{"title":"Rivendell Bicycle Sentences Book","link":"https://theradavist.com/rivendell-bicycle-sentences-book/","date":1717420367000,"content":"<p><img width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/bikesentencebook-6.jpg?fit=1200,2000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/bikesentencebook-6.jpg?w=3000&amp;quality=75 3000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/bikesentencebook-6.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/bikesentencebook-6.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/bikesentencebook-6.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/bikesentencebook-6.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/bikesentencebook-6.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Grant Petersen from Rivendell finished his <a href=\"https://www.rivbike.com/products/bicycle-sentences-book?mc_cid=e20bbac574&amp;mc_eid=d742c5b5a4\" target=\"_blank\">Bicycle Sentences book</a> and it’s in stock now for $20. It features 177 sentences about riding bicycles and bikes themselves; stuff you may know or might not know, may believe or might not. It’s not a Rule Book, not a Holy Book.</p>\n<p>“I believe them all, they’re all true for me/Grant, and some may be true for you or worth experimenting with, and who knows what else?”</p>\n<p>Check it out at <a href=\"https://www.rivbike.com/products/bicycle-sentences-book?mc_cid=e20bbac574&amp;mc_eid=d742c5b5a4\" target=\"_blank\">Rivendell</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/rivendell-bicycle-sentences-book/\">Rivendell Bicycle Sentences Book</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"901b30